videos.headline: Golden Gophers recover Badgers' fumble
videos.description: Wisconsin's Jonathan Taylor runs the ball up the middle, and is hit hard by Minnesota's Thomas Barber who forces the fumble, and is recovered by Minn Kamal.

videos.headline: Badgers' Hornibrook finds Penniston for 5-yard TD
videos.description: Alex Hornibrook completes a pass to Kyle Penniston in the end zone for another Wisconsin touchdown.

videos.headline: Davis' TD widens Badgers' lead
videos.description: Alex Hornibrook finds Danny Davis III for a 5-yard touchdown catch in the 3rd quarter.

videos.headline: Wisconsin starts 4th with 53-yard TD run
videos.description: Jonathan Taylor receives the handoff and runs 53 yards fora Badgers' touchdown.

videos.headline: Badgers' Hornibrook discusses emotions in blowout win
videos.description: Quarterback Alex Hornibrook breaks down the mental toughness of Wisconsin's program.

videos.headline: Previewing the Big Ten championship game
videos.description: ESPN's Rod Gilmore and Mark Jones break down the Wisconsin-Ohio State matchup and discuss Alex Hornibrook's performance.

videos.headline: Wisconsin blanks Minnesota
videos.description: Alex Hornibrook tosses three touchdown passes while Jonathan Taylor runs for 149 yards and a score as the No. 5 Badgers beat the Golden Gophers 31-0.
